{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "6224c5f3-abc6-4496-8f12-60130cb973aa", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6224c5f3-abc6-4496-8f12-60130cb973aa@1.pkg/1772597620105/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597620700", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6224c5f3-abc6-4496-8f12-60130cb973aa@1.pkg/1772597620105/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597620700"}, "identifier": "6224c5f3-abc6-4496-8f12-60130cb973aa", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查对 &ldquo;走向未来&rdquo; 中坚持理想、勇于担当、磨砺意志的理解。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①：</span><span>体现了以国家利益为重的担当精神，与于敏将个人力量融入祖国强盛的追求相符；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②：</span><span>强调经历磨砺才能成就事业，与于敏 28 年艰苦研发、反复试验的过程相符；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④：</span><span>突出坚韧不拔的意志，与于敏面对困难不放弃的精神相符；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>：强调集体与合作的重要性，材料中未体现这一内容，故不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>故本题选 B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>&ldquo;共和国勋章&rdquo; 获得者于敏，隐姓埋名 28 年投身氢弹研发，在艰苦的环境中反复试验，多次推翻原有方案从头再来。他曾说：&ldquo;一个人的名字，早晚是要没有的，能把微薄的力量融进祖国的强盛之中，便足以自慰了。&rdquo; 于敏的事迹体现的精神品质与下列诗句相符的是（&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span>）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>苟利国家生死以，岂因祸福避趋之</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>宝剑锋从磨砺出，梅花香自苦寒来</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>一花独放不是春，百花齐放春满园</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>千磨万击还坚劲，任尔东西南北风</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）“共和国勋章” 获得者于敏，隐姓埋名 28 年投身氢弹研发，在艰苦的环境中反复试验，多次推翻原有方案从头再来。他曾说：“一个人的名字，早晚是要没有的，能把微薄的力量融进祖国的强盛之中，便足以自慰了。” 于敏的事迹体现的精神品质与下列诗句相符的是（     ）①苟利国家生死以，岂因祸福避趋之②宝剑锋从磨砺出，梅花香自苦寒来③一花独放不是春，百花齐放春满园④千磨万击还坚劲，任尔东西南北风", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6224c5f3-abc6-4496-8f12-60130cb973aa@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984747273", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②③&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}